{"tid":1579454,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"讓「Pokemon go」變成「榮光go」「文宣go」","createTime":"2019-09-18T14:51:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T15:09:31.000Z","uid":259901,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7e084c93c7e1a189008063b4bb41f8bd97ca0515","tid":1579454,"uid":259901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:51:05.000Z","msg":"頭先落樓下商場打超夢嘅時候<br />\n突然發現pokemon go打團體戰係一個幾好嘅和理非場合，可以畀大家唱榮光或者做文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">原因：</span></span><br />\n1. 團體戰會自動幫你聚咗一大堆人埋嚟，仲限死咗佢哋一定要企係道館個位幾分鐘先打得完<br />\n一首榮光一分幾鐘就播完，入房等開波可以齊唱，打緊可以當加油，正好利用到所有gap time<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 仲有玩嘅都知道，pokemon go主力大軍係中老年阿叔阿嬸，同埋仲有好多合家歡，正好係我哋好多時候都冇法接觸到嘅「真.不問世事」和理非<br />\n而玩得pokemon go，呢個廢老廢中係廢極有限，起碼識得上網查攻略，已經秒殺你屋企果件盲塞藍絲廢老啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 可以有效過濾果啲比支共洗腦過嘅生番<br />\n因為呢個仆街地方連pokemon go都冇得玩啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 就算有仆街藍絲行過發爛渣，講真，咁多人陪緊你打道館，以武制暴有幾難<br />\n同埋玩緊pokemon go播下歌仔咁和理非仲要比支共搞，絕對可以上國際新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. 超夢真係好撚型好撚好J<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">推薦裝備：</span></span><br />\n1. 街坊look<br />\n屌你老母唔係full gear落街打道館咁on 9啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 手機download各版本榮光<br />\n<a href=\"https://archive.org/details/glorytohkmarchvermitamaster3/Glory+to+Hong+Kong+first+version.wav\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Farchive.org%2Fdetails%2Fglorytohkmarchvermitamaster3%2FGlory%2Bto%2BHong%2BKong%2Bfirst%2Bversion.wav&d=YpkAIiMN%2BbqadqYnCsWFxgzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=06f10f4c\" target=\"_blank\">https://archive.org/details/glorytohkmarchvermitamaster3/Glory+to+Hong+Kong+first+version.wav</a> <br />\n或者直接連網後台播都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 對和理非用影片/錄音<br />\n鏗鏘集，視點31，劉細良等等，隨你中意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以用<a href=\"https://www.onlinevideoconverter.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.onlinevideoconverter.com&d=YpkAIiMN%2BbqadqYnCsWFxgzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=763c9a7d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.onlinevideoconverter.com</a><br />\n將youtube片直接用mp4/mp3 down落嚟，再放落手機到拎出去播<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 藍牙喇叭<br />\n嫌細聲就拎個喇叭出去，等全個場都聽到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. 放映會設備<br />\n有心嘅可以拎成套野落去set，但時間上我覺得比較緊張，超夢蛋好似30定45分鐘前爆，未必準備得切做放映會，咁可能一部ipad就完事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n坐言不如起行<br />\n讓榮光散播到香港每一個角落！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">香港人一齊J超夢</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcd581fab981909f5839cb51338b5e6f1582b7ca","tid":1579454,"uid":259901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T15:02:25.000Z","msg":"推唔郁真係..."},{"pid":"75351188ec5e74f862bd05697322ce4a5b599b71","tid":1579454,"uid":44916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T15:07:15.000Z","msg":"裝都唔想裝，無玩好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bdeffdcae65a6282f9458aa9c98b1b552de67e8","tid":1579454,"uid":259901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75351188ec5e74f862bd05697322ce4a5b599b71","tid":1579454,"uid":44916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T15:07:15.000Z","msg":"裝都唔想裝，無玩好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T15:09:31.000Z","msg":"最近出超夢<br />\n好撚多廢老玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}